### 2. MONITOR EVENTS:
### socket.onAny((eventName, ...args) => {
###   console.log(`Event: ${eventName}`, args);
### });
###
### 3. CHECK CONNECTION:
### console.log('Connected:', socket.connected);
### console.log('Socket ID:', socket.id);
###
### 4. FORCE RECONNECT:
### socket.disconnect();
### socket.connect();
