### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### ⚠️ IMPORTANT NOTES
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###
### 1. AUTHENTICATION REQUIRED:
###    - Valid JWT token must be provided
###    - Token is verified on each connection
###    - Expired tokens cause disconnect
###
### 2. SCALABILITY:
###    - Current implementation uses in-memory storage
###    - Works for single server deployment
###    - For multi-server: Redis adapter required
###
### 3. PRIVACY:
###    - All authenticated users can see who's online
###    - Consider adding privacy settings
###    - May need friend-list filtering
###
### 4. BATTERY OPTIMIZATION:
###    - WebSocket keeps connection alive
###    - Consider disconnecting when app in background
###    - Implement smart reconnection strategy
###
### 5. DATA USAGE:
###    - Minimal data for presence updates
###    - ~1KB per user status change
###    - Consider batching updates on mobile
###
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────